spang nang 04 byams pa tshul khrims rnam rgyal/
ngag dbang blo gros rnam rgyal/
seng tshang 03 'jam dbyangs bstan pa'i nyi ma/
rdzogs chen mkhyen brtse 02 gzhon nu blo gros/
ko'u sde rdzogs chen 03 thub bstan chos kyi nyi ma/
sgo chen mkhan po dpal ldan shes rab/
chos rgyal nam mkha' nor bu/
gar dbang rgyal mchog gling pa/
gling bla sku chung rgya zil sprul sku thub bstan lung rigs rgya mtsho/
sde khri 07 'jam dbyangs bstan pa'i rgyal mtshan/
lha sprul lhun grub rgya mtsho/
'bo dkar sprul sku 02 karma nges don chos kyi blo gros/
zur mang drung pa 11 chos kyi rgya mtsho/
bya bral rin po che byams dpal 'phrin las/
dpon bla 04 blo bzang 'jigs med bstan pa'i nyi ma/
bla ma chos dbyings rdo rje/
kaHthog mkhan chen bsod nams bstan pa'i rgyal mtshan/

rje btsun blo bzang rgya mtsho dpal bzang /
klu khang zla ba tshe ring /
rong bo rab 'byams pa dge 'dun blo bzang /
seng+ge brag pa 05 ngag dbang 'gyur med chos kyi rgyal mtshan/

pad gling thugs sras 10 theg mchog bstan pa'i rgyal mtshan/

blo bzang 'jigs med bstan 'dzin rgya mtsho/

bla ma dkar po 04 blo bzang bshad sgrub bstan pa'i rgyal mtshan/
